name: I used to have the same toy
description:
This is one of my favorite photo I’ve made, I was in the Philippines in 2012 for a film shoot (yes I’m an actor), the shooting was happening in Cebu but before heading to Cebu, I had a 1 day stop in Manila.
Walking in these streets remind me my parents’ country Haïti. I’ve been in Haïti when I was a kid and here in Manila, I almost felt like home. The energy in countries in the South is similar whether you are in Asia, Africa or Latin America.
This kid was having his best time, the last time I saw these toys it was in history books at school. I was hypnotised by his passion. When I got back home, my father saw the picture and told me « Oh I used to have the same toy when I was a kid »
